# Global AI Behavior Rules

## Context & Tech Stack
- Framework: React (Vite) | Language: TypeScript | UI: Tailwind CSS
- Focus: Kingdom Kids Project Architecture.

## Token Saving & Efficiency (STRICT)
- **Conciseness:** Give code directly. Do NOT explain unless asked.
- **Partial Updates:** Use diff-style updates. Never rewrite the entire file.
- **Thinking Limit:** Stop after 3 failed attempts in Agent mode and ask me.
- **Model Usage:** Suggest "Gemini 3 Flash" for UI/simple tasks; use "Kimi k2.5" only for complex logic.

## Anti-Loop Guard
- If a terminal command fails twice, STOP and explain the error instead of retrying.